headline: Moody’s Reaffirms WSFS Financial Corp’s Baa2 Issuer Rating with a Stable Outlook; Reflects Diversified Business Model, Strong Capital, and Earnings Strength
summary: WILMINGTON, Del., August 12, 2025--Moody’s Investors Service has reaffirmed their ratings to WSFS Financial Corporation (NASDAQ: WSFS) ("WSFS" or "the Company") and WSFS Bank with issuer ratings of Baa2 with a stable outlook. Long-and short-term deposits of A2/Prime-1, together with a standalone Baseline Credit Assessment of Baa1.
